    "      \"Running statistical modeling\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Quantification results of the 1ZY9 perturbation saved to /Users/hamletkhachatryan/Desktop/DPhil_projects/pseudo/pseudo_data/1ZY9/quantify_results/k_1.25_cap_50\\n\",\n",
